skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: steph gonna steph
des: Steph Gonna Steph, originates from the term "#stephgonnasteph", which is used my Golden State Warriors fans when ever NBA player Steph Curry does something amazing. This skill provides the user with current facts, up to the 2016-2017 NBA post season/summer, about Steph Curry. These facts are both personal and basketball related.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
